\par
### When Adding New Apps:\par
\par
1. **Upload new APK to GitHub** (2 minutes)\par
2. **Copy the download link**\par
3. **Edit `app-data.json`** - add new app entry with link (3 minutes)\par
4. **Add app icon & screenshots to images folder** (2 minutes)\par
5. **Re-deploy to Netlify** - drag & drop updated folder (1 minute)\par
6. **Total time: ~10 minutes per new app**\par
\par
### When Updating Existing Apps:\par
\par
1. **Upload new version to GitHub** (replace old file or use Releases)\par
2. **Update version number in `app-data.json`**\par
3. **Update download link if filename changed**\par
4. **Re-deploy to Netlify**\par
5. **Total time: ~5 minutes**\par
